txt.en: As countless spiders flood into Cirith Ungol, it has become clear that the arrangement between the Orcs of Cirith Ungol and Shelob is at an end. If Cirith Ungol is to hold against Shelob's children, you must defeat many of the spiders that now skitter in the shadows of the fortress.
As countless spiders flood into Cirith Ungol, it has become clear that the arrangement between the Orcs of Cirith Ungol and Shelob is at an end.
